Privacy Policy

GameNot built the Mine Mob Clicker Rpg app as a Commercial app. This app is provided by GameNot and is intended for use as is.
This page is used to inform visitors regarding my policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use my app.

If you choose to use my app, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy. The data that is being saved is used to provide the app. I will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.

Information Collection and Use
I do not collect any personal identifiable information, but I use some services that might be doing so, therefore I recommend you to familiarize yourself with the following policies as well:
-Unity Ads: https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy
My app can use the device's internal memory to save the game statistics for the user, but this data will not be stored anywhere except for the device's memory and will not be transmitted to anyone over the Internet

Security
Insofar as I do not store your data in my storage, I am not responsible for its security.

Children’s Privacy
I don’t require you to provide any information when using my app and I don’t collect, share or use any information about you or your device.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
I may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. I will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about my Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact me at holds339@gmail.com. 

